\doxysubsection{Detailed Description}
This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by \mbox{\hyperlink{classit_1_1unical_1_1mat_1_1parsers_1_1datalog_1_1idlv_1_1IDLVParser}{IDLVParser}}.
